Class CondBranchInstruction

java.lang.Object
org.specs.comp.ollir.Node
org.specs.comp.ollir.Instruction
org.specs.comp.ollir.CondBranchInstruction
Direct Known Subclasses:
OpCondInstruction, SingleOpCondInstruction
public abstract class CondBranchInstruction extends Instruction
Class representing the OLLIR conditional instructions. They have a comparison and a label to which the flow must jump if the comparison is evaluated as true.
